overview:
Initial Design Consulting is a design and IT Solutions company that has been providing the Central Valley with webdesign, graphics, SEO and IT consulting since early 2006.We specialize in network setup/troubleshooting, server administration, network/pc management, and software deployment. Additionally we provide many graphic design services including flyers, business cards, templates, brochures, and even videos. If online advertising is where your business is headed, let us help you achieve this with our knowledge of Content Management Systems(CMS), HTML, CSS, XHTML, JSP, PHP, mySQL, and Perl coding.

Whether you are looking for a simple web page to showcase your business, or a flashy, full blown dynamic website featuring online sales, project management tools, and numbers of other applications, Initial Design Consulting has an affordable and effective solution for you!
